        "cooked": "<p>Right now, there’s a good balance between the glass elements and the “naked” ones on the top, as the clock, battery indicator and the contact name don’t have a glass background, while the buttons surrounding them do.</p>\n<p>However—and I’m not sure if this is an iOS system related issue or a Signal specific issue—sometimes the names don’t respond quickly enough or at all to the change in background and stay black while the rest of the elements turn white.</p>\n<p>I tried finding good screenshots that are easy to blur but still showcase the problem in a real-life scenario. Undoubtedly these examples are still on the better side but the second one maybe better illustrates that if there’s a large photo or sticker or something behind then the black names can easily turn completely invisible.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/c/e/cee651961c24c340592bb73a1f4be9b2aa91bc99.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/cee651961c24c340592bb73a1f4be9b2aa91bc99\" title=\"\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/c/e/cee651961c24c340592bb73a1f4be9b2aa91bc99_2_690x229.png\" alt=\"\" data-base62-sha1=\"twjOuIVrtGHh2g5lTnVQl1mm52V\" width=\"690\" height=\"229\" role=\"presentation\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/c/e/cee651961c24c340592bb73a1f4be9b2aa91bc99_2_690x229.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/c/e/cee651961c24c340592bb73a1f4be9b2aa91bc99_2_1035x343.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/c/e/cee651961c24c340592bb73a1f4be9b2aa91bc99.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"98AABC\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\"></span><span class=\"informations\">1179×392 118 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/0/b/0ba33804de36f9851babaeaabfd6792fe4efb348.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/0ba33804de36f9851babaeaabfd6792fe4efb348\" title=\"\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/b/0ba33804de36f9851babaeaabfd6792fe4efb348_2_690x216.png\" alt=\"\" data-base62-sha1=\"1EWWHR9RjoEknJHyVofarTWsHRC\" width=\"690\" height=\"216\" role=\"presentation\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/b/0ba33804de36f9851babaeaabfd6792fe4efb348_2_690x216.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/b/0ba33804de36f9851babaeaabfd6792fe4efb348_2_1035x324.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/0/b/0ba33804de36f9851babaeaabfd6792fe4efb348.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"919590\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\"></span><span class=\"informations\">1179×370 123 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>I wonder if reconsidering the top bar and adding a glass background somehow behind the name could remedy the issue.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/0/c/0c17ca2fe80723fe7935b2d7e47ccd3420b8f8c2.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/0c17ca2fe80723fe7935b2d7e47ccd3420b8f8c2\" title=\"\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/c/0c17ca2fe80723fe7935b2d7e47ccd3420b8f8c2_2_690x242.png\" alt=\"\" data-base62-sha1=\"1IYHl7uswqUNgFzw2ptAwmjQuiu\" width=\"690\" height=\"242\" role=\"presentation\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/c/0c17ca2fe80723fe7935b2d7e47ccd3420b8f8c2_2_690x242.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/0/c/0c17ca2fe80723fe7935b2d7e47ccd3420b8f8c2.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/0/c/0c17ca2fe80723fe7935b2d7e47ccd3420b8f8c2.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"9D8FDB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\"></span><span class=\"informations\">734×258 127 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>This is how iMessage is doing it, for reference.</p>\n<p>Telegram’s solution is also very similar, they have the name with a background in the middle and the contact photo in the place of the video call.</p>",
